title: Dakine 101 Pack
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2012 101 Pack, shown in the Fremont print.
Pack features:
- Fleece lined, padded sleeve fits most 15" laptops
- Fleece lined padded iPad sleeve
- Breathable DriMesh® back panel and shoulder straps
- Organizer pocket
- Back panel security pocket
- Fleece lined sunglass pocket
- Water bottle pocket
- Padded bottom panel
